*:G4_22
I:[22] Kurt Vonnegut
S:If you can't write clearly, you probably don't think nearly as well as you think.

*:G4_23
I:[23] James Gosling
S:You never actually find a perfect answer to a problem.  You just find the
 :answer that has the fewest problems.

*:G4_24
